## 1. Cell 1 — audit-cell / file-extension-validator

**Priority:** 1 (first to migrate — scope hẹp, no business coupling)

### Current state: **S2** `transitional-canonical-wrapper`

Evidence:
- `src/cells/kernel/audit-cell/scanner/file-extension-validator.khai` (canonical)
- `src/cells/kernel/audit-cell/scanner/file-extension-validator.ts` (substrate)
- `src/cells/kernel/audit-cell/contracts/file-extension-validator.interface.khai` + `.ts`
- `nattos.sh §40` gọi `npx tsx` vào `.ts` directly (bypass canonical — per RUNTIME_DEPENDENCY_CENSUS §2.1)

### Required header (apply vào `.khai` file):

```
@state: S2
@canonical: src/cells/kernel/audit-cell/scanner/file-extension-validator.khai
@substrate: src/cells/kernel/audit-cell/scanner/file-extension-validator.ts
@since: 2026-04-23
```

### Transition S2 → S3 conditions (Kim SPEC §2.2):

1. Substrate cell-hóa: audit-cell đã có boundary guard (`src/cells/kernel/audit-cell/audit-cell.boundary.si` — **evidence: exists**)
2. Canonical gọi qua EventBus L2 Mạch HeyNa, không import `.ts` trực tiếp
3. `nattos.sh §40` patch: bỏ `npx tsx` direct call, route qua Host
4. Audit trail ghi nhận quá trình tách (audit-chain contract Kim existing)

### @bridge target (post-S3):

`@bridge: audit-cell::file-extension-validator`

### Rollback: `rbf_s2_wrapper` — giữ nguyên S2 behavior, restore `npx tsx` call

